1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
Once upon a time, a young scholar lived in a village.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:09,000
Every day he studied, reading books under the pine tree.

3
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:14,000
One day, he decided to travel to Hanyang for the civil exam.

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:18,000
After a long journey, the scholar finally arrived in Hanyang.

5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:23,000
Standing before the palace, he marveled at its grandeur.

6
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:27,000
The exam hall was filled with scholars from across the land.

7
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:32,000
The scholar poured all his effort into writing the exam.

8
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:36,000
At last, the day of the results arrived.

9
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:41,000
The scholar earned first place and became the pride of his village.

10
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:45,000
And so, the scholar became a great official serving the people.
